seo: 大唐AC,默认密码,漏洞检测,CNVD-2021-04128,弱口令
summary: 该插件用于检测大唐AC设备是否存在CNVD-2021-04128漏洞，即默认弱口令问题（用户名：admin，密码：123456）
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the Datang AC device has the CNVD-2021-04128 vulnerability, which is the issue of default weak password (username: admin, password: 123456)
